{"tid":1114693,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"茶餐廳有師奶評論安心事件都幾高質","createTime":"2019-04-18T15:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T08:29:04.000Z","uid":228934,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe6fd192ed6fc5f88e14144cd451dd40fafb7461","tid":1114693,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:20:07.000Z","msg":"下晝三點三幾個等湊放學嘅師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘆住但他凍奶茶喺度講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得都幾高質<br />\n<br />\n師奶話一向見黃心穎笑得咁甜咗覺得佢應該好純品好乖女， 娶新抱都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，冇諗過原來佢咁鍾意講粗口。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住梗係有人話係人梗係虛偽㗎喇，不過心穎個樣咁乖，真係估唔到粗口爛舌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢而家啲小朋友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />世風日下公眾地方原來可以咁主動對一個大自己三十年嘅男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好得人驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋都要小心啲呀"},{"pid":"41ce9222c2c4dd92821d11d92b4cc7a65ab53aa6","tid":1114693,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:20:58.000Z","msg":"班師奶咪又係臭雞"},{"pid":"3f0f54e1702ef12912c60dd6739e2fc8fc1d0d28","tid":1114693,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T15:22:21.000Z","msg":"黃心穎三張嘢都係小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245ddb9fa1cffdc2f2917433cd2be854f4615de2","tid":1114693,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"